        },
        "reasoning": {
          "whyChosen": "App Service is the simplest PaaS compute for web apps on Azure, with built-in scaling, TLS, and managed runtimes.",
          "alternativesConsidered": [
            "Container Apps ŌĆö better for microservices/containers, more complex",
            "Azure VM ŌĆö full control but higher operational burden",
            "Static Web App ŌĆö only for static/JAMstack sites"
